{"tid":1001636,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"投訴Air Max鞋底商標似「阿拉」批侮辱　穆斯林促下架","createTime":"2019-01-30T09:54:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-30T12:00:44.000Z","uid":75969,"like":2,"dislike":36,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"be910109679408ee808ded6ec41c6b5d176666d4","tid":1001636,"uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T09:54:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20190130/s00005/2b8a4d23a20e811c7cfcfae289cc4837.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20190130%2Fs00005%2F2b8a4d23a20e811c7cfcfae289cc4837.jpg&h=acd1003a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n運動品牌Nike的Air Max系列商標近日被指侮辱穆斯林，有人不滿Air Max商標倒轉後和「阿拉」的阿拉伯文寫法相近，抗議Nike將該標誌印於鞋底。Nike否認指控，表示該商標只代表Air Max，並無其他含意。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://近日有人於請願網站Change.org\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E8%BF%91%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%89%E4%BA%BA%E6%96%BC%E8%AB%8B%E9%A1%98%E7%B6%B2%E7%AB%99Change.org&d=CddLi1wVc%2F0RDzQLDYdfB%2F4FZ2Hvuo87ztF5QEQ%2B7nM%3D&h=9d8c74ab\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">近日有人於請願網站Change.org</a>發起請願，指Nike的Air Max系列商標倒轉跟阿拉伯文的「阿拉」字眼相似，而該商標印於多款運動鞋鞋底，疑有侮辱穆斯林之嫌。請願發起人Saiqa Noreen表示，Nike將神的名字印於鞋底令人髮指，又指摘Nike「不尊重及極度冒犯伊斯蘭教」。Noreen要求Nike回收所有印有該商標的鞋，以及日後嚴格規管產品。該請願目標獲15,000人聯署，而截至今日下午，該請願已有逾12,000人聯署。<br />\n<br />\nNike回應表示，公司尊重所有宗教並嚴肅看待事件，強調該標誌只是Air Max的商標，並無其他含意。<br />\n<br />\n美國伊斯蘭關係理事會董事霍柏（Ibrahim Hooper）表示已向Nike反映事件，並希望可跟Nike公開對話。<br />\n<br />\n(Today/太陽報)<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/國際/article/20190130/s00005/1548838284836/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B%2Farticle%2F20190130%2Fs00005%2F1548838284836%2F&d=CddLi1wVc%2F0RDzQLDYdfB%2F4FZ2Hvuo87ztF5QEQ%2B7nM%3D&h=48dd3e96\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B%2Farticle%2F20190130%2Fs00005%2F1548838284836%2F&h=b90a5fb6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/國際/article/20190130/s00005/1548838284836/</a>"},{"pid":"28a0a00f13dbd92b915c1eb4c6eaa102b92d5ae3","tid":1001636,"uid":201823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T09:55:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18300d769d623b7a05f107b303a4cb7d40ebc7c0","tid":1001636,"uid":224952,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T09:56:42.000Z","msg":"咁全世界有W呀M既logo都要收皮喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b29573b7ad0dfb8012fa806342b8866bb1a2b32","tid":1001636,"uid":9726,"like":37,"dislike":0,"score":37,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T09:58:36.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f6bed30af75618c00af579d9493bfcfe93ca04e3","tid":1001636,"uid":673,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"18300d769d623b7a05f107b303a4cb7d40ebc7c0","tid":1001636,"uid":224952,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T09:56:42.000Z","msg":"咁全世界有W呀M既logo都要收皮喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T09:58:36.000Z","msg":"佢咁樣圈出黎又真係幾似樣既"},{"pid":"46a61e3969fbe0faf61fc6eb2c1785937cde0f31","tid":1001636,"uid":10757,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T09:59:13.000Z","msg":"過多幾年出現返十字軍東征我都覺得唔奇"},{"pid":"cb0a3a10f156c6240426c8390e5b79974c520610","tid":1001636,"uid":2752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T10:05:06.000Z","msg":"咁全世界都唔用得VWI連埋做商標<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e9276988d88331c30d1f4d39b8d8685486630c8","tid":1001636,"uid":179409,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"f6bed30af75618c00af579d9493bfcfe93ca04e3","tid":1001636,"uid":673,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"18300d769d623b7a05f107b303a4cb7d40ebc7c0","tid":1001636,"uid":224952,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T09:56:42.000Z","msg":"咁全世界有W呀M既logo都要收皮喎<img src=\"